          "type": "npc_line",
          "speakerId": "SYSTEM",
          "text": "Declaiming requires a signed exclusion list and a physical placement boundary.\nThe placement boundary must be marked with tape of an approved color.\nThe approved color is listed in Appendix D, which is currently unavailable on this terminal.",
